<div class="component  component--is-in-another-component">

  
  <div class="component-text-block">
  
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="focus-on-the-user" class="__title invisible">Focus on the user</h2>
                    </div>

  
  <p>User needs drive all of the content and services that make up the web presence. All web content and services are regularly assessed through user testing and use data. Areas of the web presence that do not meet the standards of our users are retired or improved.</p>



  
</div>

  
</div>

    

</div>
          </div>
      </dd>

    <dt class="component-accordion__title"
          role="heading"
          aria-level="2">
        <button
          class="component-accordion__button js-toggle-acc"
